Endotronics Inc, halted at 1-3/4 onNASDAQ pending release of a news report, on Monday said it wasexpecting "substantial losses" for the quarter ending March 31,1987 and the fiscal year ending Sept 30, 1987.    The company had cited a dispute over payment by Yamaha Inc,one of its Japanese distributors, over payment of a promissorynote for 3,686,000 dlrs in overdue accounts. Reuter&#3;